<!--
# Simple Action - Writing Your Own Action

A named entity carrying the `SayHello` action, which reads the caller entity's
`Name` off the async world and greets it, then passes. `{RunOnLoad}` runs it on
load, then exits.

    beet --main=examples/action/simple_action.bsx
-->
<Name("greeter") {(SayHello, RunOnLoad)}/>
